Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.85,0:22:44.36,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}They make the children really ring
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.41,0:22:49.81,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}I spend the day your way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.81,0:22:56.38,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}Call it morning driving thru the sound and in and out the valley
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.38,0:22:59.04,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}In and around the lake
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.09,0:23:04.20,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}Mountains come out of the sky and they stand there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.17,0:23:10.96,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}One mile over we'll be there and we'll see you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.59,0:23:17.39,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}Ten true summers we'll be there and laughing too
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.08,0:23:25.69,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}Twenty four before my love you'll see I'll be there with you
