Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.09,0:23:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,690)\fad(300,300)}冷酷！殘忍！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.51,0:23:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,690)\fad(300,300)}我要打倒你！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.31,0:23:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,690)\fad(300,300)}很好 你有足夠的資格死在我瓦姆烏手下！
